isk, making satellite-formation less likely,\nif $\\mathrm{M_p} \\gtrsim 5 \\mathrm{M_{Jup}}$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 23 May 2017 17:59:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-06-28"}
