ce and factor complexity\nfunctions of subshifts generated by marked substitutions. We describe these\nfunctions in particular detail for the generalized Thue-Morse substitutions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 24 May 2017 13:23:17 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 5 Sep 2018 13:54:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-09-17"}
